            <h1>The War Game</h1>
            <p style="font-family: Kumbh Sans"><span style="color: #b30000; font-family: Lemon Milk;">War.</span> is a simulation game based off of World War I. This game pits country against country in a struggle for power across a vast region. Alliances, negotiations, and distribution of the spoils of victory are all essential to staying alive in the game. But beware...not even alliances are safe from sabotage.</p>
